Given	I'm logged-in with valid credentials
When I select 'Male' radio button from Page 01 of Pelvic MRI
And I select any Examination radio button from Page 01 of Pelvic MRI
And I select 'Individual' radio button from Sequences box on Page 03
And I select 'DWI' from 'Weighting' dropdown menu
And I go to Page 04 of Pelvic MRI
And I click on 'Finding' tab
And I click on 'Finding' radio button

When I select 'Lesion TZ' from 'Finding' dropdown menu
Then 'Add new finding' button is enabled
And 'Characterization I' tab is enabled and preselected
And 'Characterization II' tab is enabled
And 'Size/PIRADS Score' tab is enabled

When 'Characterization I' tab is selected
Then a multiple selection localizer is enabled

And 'Increase' radio button is enabled
And 'Reduction' radio button is enabled

And 'Circumscribed' radio button is enabled
And 'Non-circumscribed' radio button is enabled

And 'Homogeneous' radio button is enabled
And 'Heterogeneous' radio button is enabled

And 'Completely encapsulated' radio button is enabled
And 'Partially encapsulated (mostly)' radio button is enabled
And 'No capsule' radio button is enabled

And 'Anterior fibromuscular stroma' checkbox is enabled
And 'Central zone' checkbox is enabled
And 'Ejaculatory duct' checkbox is enabled
And 'Prostatic urethra' checkbox is enabled

And 'Lentiform' checkbox is enabled
And 'Spiculated' checkbox is enabled
And '"Erased charcoal sign”/“smudgy fingerprint"' checkbox is enabled
And 'Typical BPH nodes' checkbox is enabled

And 'Increased DWI signal' checkbox is enabled
And 'ADC hypointensity' checkbox is enabled

When I click on the localizer
And I click on 'TZ Base right anterior' zone
And I click on 'TZ Base right posterior' zone
Then 'TZ Base right anterior' zone is selected
And 'TZ Base right posterior' zone is selected

When I select 'Reduction' radio button
Then 'Signal loss/flow void' checkbox is enabled

When I select 'Ejaculatory duct' checkbox
Then 'Right' radio button is enabled
And 'Left' radio button is enabled

When I select 'Increased DWI signal' checkbox
Then 'Discrete' radio button is enabled
And 'Pronounced' radio button is enabled
When I select 'Discrete' radio button
Then 'Linear/triangular' radio button is enabled
And 'Focal' radio button is enabled

When I select 'ADC hypointensity' checkbox
Then 'Discrete' radio button is enabled
And 'Pronounced' radio button is enabled
When I select 'Discrete' radio button
Then 'Linear/triangular' radio button is enabled
And 'Focal' radio button is enabled
